column6: "GONE NATIVE" PART 1 OF 4! Runaways fans alert: This issue focuses on Nico…and her newly resurrected evil ex-boyfriend, Alex! Oh, and something really bad has happened to fellow Runaway Chase! Why are we so mean? Plus: What happened to Cammi? Only Baron Zemo knows…
column8: | writer:Dennis Hopeless | penciller (cover):Francesco Mattina | artist:Kev Walker
